title: The Best American Sports Writing 2014
description:
Christopher McDougall, Glenn Stout, "The Best American Sports Writing 2014"

ISBN: 0544147006 | 2014 | EPUB/PDF | 416 pages | 3 MB


"Excellent . . . A no-brainer pickup for the sports collection." -- Booklist

"An affirmation of the strong state of American sportswriting." -- Kirkus Reviews
From more than 350 national, regional, and specialty publications and, increasingly, top online publishers, Christopher McDougall, best-selling author of Born to Run: A Hidden Tribe, Superathletes, and the Greatest Race the World Has Never Seen, hand-selected the very best sports journalism of the past year
